---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Spring Testing Framework
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Unit Testing
spring provides several mock objects to help testing in isolation
- Environment, PropertySource, JNDI, Servlet
- Reactive: ServerHttpRequest, ServerHttpResponse

# Integration Testing
spring provides
- managing Spring Ioc container - DI of test instances
- transaction management
- base classes

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
spring-boot-starter-test
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
provides several testing frameworks
- JUnit, Hamcrest
- AssertJ
- Mockito
- JsonPath, JsonAssert